{
  "stem": "21013.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The battles were so terrible, especially on the border of Italy, that in the-- at the last moment, from what I have heard, they took 15- and 16-year-old boys and 70-year-old men.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was called the [NON-ENGLISH], the last effort, you know, where they took anybody that could still walk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got this good job, you know, as a traffic manager, which was a very good job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father was very educated and extremely verbal and personable, so-- but he didn't have much common sense when it came to the time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he didn't want to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I said, my only occupation at that time was to find a way to get out of Austria.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a constant quest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took every day walking on the streets being afraid that you would be accosted or taken to jail or murdered or goodness knows what.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother never knew whether I was ever going to come home again after I left in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would talk to some other young people that were doing the same thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- there was really no chance for them to go with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I got the affidavits, that was only for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was young, these people whose name was Harmel-- it turned out that they were all related to each other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they knew that the other people had also sent affidavits.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they combined and they forwarded their affidavits to a daughter of the man in Washington, whose husband was a famous patent attorney in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had a daughter my age, so they thought it would be perfect if I would come and be a ready-made sister for her.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
